UNIVERSAL TEXTIL said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 12.19% to NT$185,549,000 from NT$211,312,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            185,549          211,312    
YOY%             -12.19%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            713,292          762,266    
YOY%              -6.42% 
=================================================================
 